column5: thanks GB it was real nice to get out.....
I woulda joined you... if I hadn't been under my '98 GMC changing a starter! *($#($*#  Now where are the pics/report?

and a Crap Dinner it was.....    Your welcome Terry anytime.  Im sure Ill be up that way again very soon Wayne. I'm out of crap it seems and full of it to.  Sorry if I talked your ears off Terry...  I had TONS more to talk about....hahahahahaha....

It was definitely a nice morning out there, a little slushy to say the least  It was nice meeting you Terry, i'll have to sharpen those blades on the auger for you guys next time  Always a pleasure fishing with GB....aka.....Chatty Cathy
AH ,Terry brought his auger eh.LOL

ya...  ..the blades....ya...  ..OR...Next time maybe I can bring my own auger instead of telling Terry to leave his at home.....OOOPS!!! Ah well there's a first time for everything...and a second and third...  Thanks Marty for the use of the Auger.
dang, that looks good, AzuluSpookd nice meeting you too   auger..I only have my gas auger with the 8" or 10" hole ,whatever size it is..might have been over kill
Why am I not surprised,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,     So tell me,how far did you walk?
not ever far but I didn't wear those big heavy boot I wear most times

no I didn't get fired  I had to use up my unused vacation days..so I'm off work from right now  till jan 7 08  guess I should go fishing...  maybe half a day of honey do list and maybe some more fishing and squeeze in xmas too life is tough, but I will make the most of it
atta boy!
Piss off will ya. HOZER
Oh did I mention I got to work the holidays,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,double and triple the pay does help sooth the pain.LOL
i got to get on one of those plans...
government job..got to love it..LOL   triple the pay..you they need some help over the holidays....
Terry: I've got 2 days left to work than off until the 2nd of Jan. And I thought I had it pretty good.  :rolleyes:  Enjoy your time off: Rick
Your already over paid.LOL J/K
so what are you trying to say  are you trying to bring me down.......LOL   Woodsman, enjoy the time off..get some fishing in
See... there's one of them civil servants I wuz talkin about ! LOL  Enjoy the time off Bud...but make sure you've worked enough in the new year to get a few more days off come February!!!!

Geez and I thought teachers had it made  Enjoy the holidays Terry!  And work hard there Brian! With all that extra dough you'll be able to buy another boat for downrigging again!  Have a great Christmas guys,  Rob
hey, Wayne watch    what you say    there is nothing civil about me......   and no problem come Jan first a whole new batch of  vacation days and another 26 sick days  I can use, so I am ready

I've been off since friday......till Jan. 7th. Getting in a couple last minute duck hunts, then its time to hit the hardwater.  maybe I'll run into  you out there someplace. i've got a green eskimo quickflip, behind an arctic cat puma.  Sinker
Nice Terry. Enjoy it. I'm "out of work" at the moment too. Which translates to "stay home and don't get paid". Yup. Us unionized guys have it made.
Very nice Terry! After changing jobs in October, I'm looking forward to some upcomming time off myself. I have to go until this Friday, but then I'm off till Jan. 7th as well. Enjoy!
Hey Terry you up ?????????????????? I got some snow banks you can SHOVEL away.
ahhhhhh, I will pass but thanks.....LOL  maybe I will see some of you on the ice this is my set up
What ever you guys do,dont ask whats in the yellow bag. Lets just say all he,s missing is the kitchen sink.LOL  Play safe out there friend.
Whats in the Yellow bag?
Terry. How come yer not fishing today?

now lets, see  fishfinder underwater camera digi camera coffee lures and kitchen sink    today was honey do list day but tomorrow ..well I still have no plans, I guess the warmer weather hasn't hurt the ice too much..might get out tomorrow
Into some Crappy fishing maybe? I was thinking about going for the morning.
hey maybe I can make it I do have to be somewhere in the after noon but might be able to do a morning thing
IT's dinner time. Was fun. Good morning out. Ill post a shot of the feed....lol  Nice to have TIME OFF to fish,,
Ahhhhhhhhhh, the old, rub it in thing eh GB. LOL
